H3.text: A wisp or walk is the collective noun for which group of birds? Latin name gallinago gallinago.. Snipe

A4.text: A snipe is any of about 26 wading bird species in three genera in the family Scolopacidae.

A5.text: The snipe's bill allows the very tip to remain closed while the snipe slurps up invertebrates.
